neodba %s

A Neovim plugin to interact with databases.

USAGE: neodba [<OPTIONS>] [<SQL><NIL>]

OPTIONS:

--log-level [FATAL|ERROR|WARN|SUCCESS|INFO|DEBUG|TRACE]
  Specify the log level
  The default value is INFO

--help, -h
  Show this help

--version
  Show current version

<SQL>

When arguments are provided it is intrepreted as a SQL statement to execute.
For example:

  neodba select * from users

<NIL>

When no arguments are provided SQL statements are read from stdin.
